import React, { useState } from "react";

import { Box, Grid, TextField, Button } from "@material-ui/core";
import HeaderTask from "./../Home/Tasks/HeaderTask";

export default function Profile() {
  const [inputValue, setInputValue] = useState({
    username: "",
    email: "",
    firstName: "",
    lastName: "",
    city: "",
    country: "",
    postalCode: "",
    about: "",
  });

  const onChange = (e) => {
    var name = e.target.name;
    var value = e.target.value;

    setInputValue({
      [name]: value,
    });
  };

  return (
    <Box className="body-admin m-0 pt-5 bgr-admin" sx={{ minHeight: "100vh" }}>
      <Grid container spacing={1} className="ps-4 w-100">
        <Grid item xs={8}>
          <Box className="box">
            <HeaderTask
              bgr="badge-purple"
              title="Edit Profile"
              position="start"
              caption="Complete your profile"
            />
            <Grid container spacing={2} className="py-4 px-3">
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField
                  label="Company"
                  defaultValue="How2Code"
                  disabled
                  variant="standard"
                  className="w-100"
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={3}>
                <TextField
                  color="secondary"
                  label="Username"
                  value={inputValue.username}
                  onChange={onChange()}
                  variant="standard"
                  className="w-100"
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={3}>
                <TextField
                  label="Email address"
                  color="secondary"
                  variant="standard"
                  className="w-100"
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField
                  label="First Name"
                  color="secondary"
                  variant="standard"
                  className="w-100"
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField
                  label="Last Name"
                  color="secondary"
                  variant="standard"
                  className="w-100"
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}>
                <TextField
                  label="City"
                  color="secondary"
                  variant="standard"
                  className="w-100"
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}>
                <TextField
                  label="Country"
                  color="secondary"
                  variant="standard"
                  className="w-100"
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}>
                <TextField
                  label="Postal Code"
                  color="secondary"
                  variant="standard"
                  className="w-100"
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={12}>
                <TextField
                  label="About me"
                  color="secondary"
                  variant="standard"
                  className="w-100"
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={12} className="mt-3">
                <Button variant="contained" color="secondary">
                  UPDATE PROFILE
                </Button>
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Box>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={4}></Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Box>
  );
}
